Package org.stuntaz.libqcw.blobs.workspace

Support for parsing and writing workspaces.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
SectionContainerBlob Represents a section container blob.
SectionHeaderBlob Represents the section header blob that contains multiple entries of SectionHeaderInfoBlob instances.
SectionHeaderInfoBlob Represents the blob which specifies information about a single section present in the workspace.
SectionNumberBlob Represents the blob which specifies the number of sections in a workspace blob.
WorkspaceBlob Represents a workspace blob TODO: Create easier-to-use workspace section API Reasoning: The various blobs that comprise the workspace section are currently implemented very literally (one per actual blob).
